64bc7cffd3e6"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "> ",
 StyleBox["BarChart[sortTally[[All,2]]/1000,ChartLabels->sortTally[[All,1]],\
AxesLabel->{\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]number of times we win\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote],\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]relative frequency\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]}] ",
